name: Warung Makan New Pogot
address: HF87+WWG, Pering Sari, Selat, Karangasem Regency, Bali 80862, Indonesia
review 1: It's conveniently along the way to sightseeing places. Food is decent and for a very good price. Nothing scenic in the area. Nice people and good service.
review 2:
Local warung by the side of main road on the way from Besakih to Lempuyang, serving chicken rice.
Great food, especially the soup. Tasted better than in Ubud. Friendly people.
3 sets of rice and 1 drink costs similar to 1 set of rice in Ubud.

review 4:
The best food I‚Äôve had in Bali so far! Very nice owner and extremely friendly wife and children too!

review 5:
Stumbled upon them during a storm. Found loving refuge as well as lovely food. Owners took good care of us and made sure the storm doesn't flush us away. We're wet as rats, but their hot tea filled us anew.

Good luck with everything! :)
